text: Peter Jutzeler (9 May 1940 - 28 September 2020) was a Swiss wrestler. He competed at the 1964 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Swiss male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Switzerland Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from the canton of Zürich
